OL,3,CFamilies remember Dunblane victims on
OL,4,C30th anniversary of school shooting
OL,6,FResidents of Dunblane are marking 30
OL,7,Fyears since the UK's deadliest school
OL,8,Fshooting, which claimed the lives of
OL,9,F16 children and a teacher. ITV News
OL,10,FCorrespondent Peter Smith reports.
OL,12,FWords by Deputy Content Editor Jessica
OL,13,FHodge
OL,15,FIt has been 30 years, but the mere
OL,16,Fmention of Dunblane still evokes a
OL,17,Fparticular horror in those old enough
OL,18,Fto remember what happened on March 13,
OL,19,F1996.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
