OL,3,CFamilies remember Dunblane victims on
OL,4,C30th anniversary of school shooting
OL,6,FThat day, 16 children and their
OL,7,Fteacher were murdered when a gunman
OL,8,Fentered their primary school,
OL,9,Ftargeting a P1 class in the gym hall.
OL,11,FThis is still the deadliest mass
OL,12,Fshooting in UK history, and led to a
OL,13,Fban on handguns in the UK.
OL,15,FOn this 30th anniversary, Mick North,
OL,16,Ffather of Sophie North, said he has
OL,17,Ftried to get his life back, but the
OL,18,Fevents of that day will never leave
OL,19,Fhim.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
