OL,3,CFamilies remember Dunblane victims on
OL,4,C30th anniversary of school shooting
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"There's probably never a day that
OL,12,Fgoes by without a brief thought about
OL,13,FSophie," he said. "And that means
OL,14,Fprobably a brief thought about what
OL,15,Fhappened in 1996."
OL,17,FHe also spoke about his work on
OL,18,Fsecuring stricter gun laws as part of
OL,19,Fthe Snowdrop campaign, saying: "I've
OL,20,Fnever reached a point where I think
OL,21,Fthe issue can be let go.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
