OL,3,CFamilies remember Dunblane victims on
OL,4,C30th anniversary of school shooting
OL,6,FOn this anniversary, some of the
OL,7,FDunblane families are trying to trace
OL,8,Fsome of the items that have been lost
OL,9,Fover the years.
OL,11,FThe community of Aberfan, which lost
OL,12,F116 children in the 1960s when a
OL,13,Fcolliery spoil tip collapsed, sent a
OL,14,Fminer's lamp to the town of Dunblane
OL,15,Fas a sign of their respect and to mark
OL,16,Fa shared grief.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
