OL,3,CFamilies remember Dunblane victims on
OL,4,C30th anniversary of school shooting
OL,6,FOn this anniversary, we were with them
OL,7,Fto open boxes that had been sealed
OL,8,Fshut for decades.
OL,10,FPam Ross, mother of Joanna Ross, told
OL,11,Fus why she decided to trace some of
OL,12,Fthe items so many years later.
OL,14,FShe said: "A bench had been made, and
OL,15,FI had no knowledge of it. It led to me
OL,16,Fthinking... What else is there?"
OL,18,F"To have these items and show the hope
OL,19,Fit gave us through their love, that's
OL,20,Fjust not something we will forget.
OL,21,FEver."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
