CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773421880
OL,3,CFamilies remember Dunblane victims on
OL,4,C30th anniversary of school shooting
OL,6,FJennifer Stirton, who's mother Eileen
OL,7,FHarrild was injured in the shooting
OL,8,Fand survived, is working with Pam to
OL,9,Ftrack down the missing items.
OL,11,FShe said: "We need to share these
OL,12,Fthings and make them available to
OL,13,Fpeople, to make them understand this
OL,14,Fis part of what happened, there was
OL,15,Fthe incident then this support".
OL,17,FNow they are seeking help and finance
OL,18,Fto create a permanent display of these
OL,19,Fitems in Dunblane, as a reminder of
OL,20,Fthe love and support sent from around
OL,21,Fthe world in their time of need.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
